# Excludes for `railway up`. Railway honours this in addition to .gitignore.
# .gitignore already excludes node_modules, .yarn caches, dist, build, etc.
#
# IMPORTANT: every entry under packages/ in package.json `workspaces` must be
# uploaded — yarn install requires each workspace's package.json. Excluding
# any of them breaks resolution of transitive type/dev deps (e.g.
# @types/lodash.camelcase on twenty-shared) and the Dockerfile build fails.
#
# We only drop the .git history (~385 MB) and obviously-unused dirs.

.git
.github
.idea
.vscode
*.log
